  "response_text": "A woman stands in a brightly lit Kohl’s clothing department, facing forward among racks of neatly hung clothes. She appears to be an adult with shoulder-length reddish-brown hair, fair skin, and a friendly, animated expression. She wears a green sweater with narrow white horizontal stripes over a crisp white collared shirt, with a dark crossbody strap running diagonally across her chest. Behind her, soft-focus displays of folded and hanging clothing fill the store, including neutral-toned sweaters and pants on racks. She smiles broadly, her shoulders lifting slightly as if excited, then settles into a pleased grin while looking toward the viewer.\n\nA bold graphic appears beside her on the left: “KOHL’S MOM” in large white letters, framed by bright red parenthesis-like shapes. The store background remains behind her as she continues smiling.\n\nThe scene shifts to a full-screen sale graphic with a hot pink and deep red background made of overlapping blocks and diagonal shadow shapes. Large white text reads “END-OF-SEASON” with “EVENT” beneath it. Faint repeated outlines of the word “DEALS” appear along the right side, and a thin line of small legal disclaimer text runs along the bottom.\n\nThe sale message changes to “SAVE UP TO 50%” in very large white lettering centered on the same pink and red background. Around the text, product photos begin appearing in a grid-like arrangement: folded sweaters in beige, blue, and gray; brown ankle boots; shiny holiday ornaments and small seasonal decorations; a pale blue turtleneck with other tops on hangers; storage baskets and bins; a white handbag; folded pants; a brown crossbody purse; a plaid blanket with a white pom-pom hat; children’s outfits; stacks of folded towels or blankets; and tall drink bottles or tumblers. The products are shown as separate rectangular cutouts surrounding the central “SAVE UP TO 50%” offer. A fine-print disclaimer remains at the bottom.\n\nThe product images then shrink and move outward, leaving more open pink space around the central “SAVE UP TO 50%” text. The commercial transitions to another bold sale screen. Huge white letters across the top-left read “CLEARANCE,” again on the hot pink and deep red geometric background with faint repeated “DEALS” text on the right. The offer builds in stages underneath: first “SAVE,” then “85%,” and finally the complete message “SAVE UP TO 85% AFTER AN EXTRA 50% OFF.” A small line of legal text stays along the bottom edge as the final clearance offer fills the screen.",
